{"tid":1955224,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"菲律賓總統：警察可以槍殺任何違反封城隔離令的人","createTime":"2020-04-02T10:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T12:22:18.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b7fbed799822c07cabee460617e22e0fba9b9fdf","tid":1955224,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"菲律賓總統杜特爾特昨晚發表電視講話，表明會嚴厲執行隔離措施，如果有人違反封城令，警方及軍人可以開槍射殺這些搞事者。另外，當局要求呂宋島居民出門須戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特警告已經下令對於違反封鎖隔離措施的人，如果不守規矩並被證明對執法人員的生命構成威脅，軍警可將他們射殺及收監。他聲言，不會讓違規者製造混亂，而會將他們埋了。<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特又表示，如果民眾不遵守秩序，當局不會向民眾派發食物援助等物資。杜特爾特同時強調，將救援物資中飽私囊的人亦會遭到嚴厲懲罰。他重申在疫情下，保持秩序非常重要，促請民眾聽從政府命令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1738344/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%9D%9C%E7%89%B9%E7%88%BE%E7%89%B9-%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD-%E8%BB%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%AF%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E5%B0%84%E6%AE%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1738344%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E6%259D%259C%25E7%2589%25B9%25E7%2588%25BE%25E7%2589%25B9-%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%258E%25AA%25E6%2596%25BD-%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%25AE%25BA&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=6239124b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1738344%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E6%259D%259C%25E7%2589%25B9%25E7%2588%25BE%25E7%2589%25B9-%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%258E%25AA%25E6%2596%25BD-%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%25AE%25BA&h=45e33693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.